race.comment: TAVROS (16) underrated gelding racing in career best form. Backed up his good Dubbo Cup placing with an eye catching third over 1600m in the Coonamble Cup with the 57.5kg. Maps well on the limit and goes close. HOLLYWOOD HERO (5) best form is over this trip, and he has a tidy second-up record. Unwanted in betting when a slashing sixth over 1400m at this track. Regular rider sticks and capable of figuring prominently. GREEN SHADOWS (7) improving with racing and desperate for the mile now. Drawn off the track at his last two starts and Schiller looks to have a few more options from the inside draw. Will be savaging the line late. BARAZIN (11) drops in trip with the blinkers going on after coming out of the pack with a solid second over 2000m at Taree. Will drift back from the gate and be ridden for luck.
